Hardware:

STM32F4 discovery board
Fastrax UP501 GPS

wire GPS PPS pin to PA1 on the STM32F4 board
wire GPS serial to GPS RX=PA2, GPS TX=PA3
wire power of GPS to a 3.3V supply (STM32F4 "3V" is 2.9V, and will not work)


Build environment:

summon-arm-toolchain - https://github.com/esden/summon-arm-toolchain.git
perl


Source code:

start by looking through src/main.c, src/pps.c, src/mytimer.c, src/uart.c


Results:

see http://dan.drown.org/stm32/run4.html
